(3429, 467, '_bbp_akismet_as_submitted', 'a:76:{s:14:"comment_author";s:4:"Ryan";s:20:"comment_author_email";s:17:"rjfrizz@gmail.com";s:18:"comment_author_url";s:9:"http://35";s:15:"comment_content";s:491:"Hi Erick,\n\nNo problem.  I add all kinds of venues from cafes to big venues on StageBanter.  Although I haven''t had time to research and add every canadian venue, so don''t assume that the venues on here are the only ones possible, there might be others.  Promoters and other bands might be able to suggest some.\n\n\nSome venues are open to new acts and others less so, but there''s no harm in asking if they''ll have you.  Try to link up with local bands that might fit well with your band.\n\nRyan";s:15:"comment_post_ID";i:456;s:12:"comment_type";s:5:"reply";s:9:"permalink";s:46:"http://stagebanter.ca/forums/topic/montreal-2/";s:8:"referrer";s:46:"http://stagebanter.ca/forums/topic/montreal-2/";s:10:"user_agent";s:119:"Mozilla/5.0 (Macintosh; Intel Mac OS X 10_8_3) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/28.0.1500.71 Safari/537.36";s:7:"user_ID";i:1;s:7:"user_ip";s:14:"74.116.191.122";s:9:"user_role";s:42:"administrator,backwpup_admin,bbp_keymaster";s:4:"blog";s:21:"http://stagebanter.ca";s:12:"blog_charset";s:5:"UTF-8";s:9:"blog_lang";s:5:"en_US";s:22:"POST_bbp_reply_content";s:498:"Hi Erick,\r\n\r\nNo problem.  I add all kinds of venues from cafes to big venues on StageBanter.  Although I haven''t had time to research and add every canadian venue, so don''t assume that the venues on here are the only ones possible, there might be others.  Promoters and other bands might be able to suggest some.\r\n\r\n\r\nSome venues are open to new acts and others less so, but there''s no harm in asking if they''ll have you.  Try to link up with local bands that might fit well with your band.\r\n\r\nRyan";s:19:"POST_bbp_topic_tags";s:18:"Montreal, Promoter";s:27:"POST_bbp_topic_subscription";s:13:"bbp_subscribe";s:21:"POST_bbp_reply_submit";s:0:"";s:20:"POST_bbp_reply_tit