(13, 1, '2012-11-03 16:46:27', '2012-11-03 20:46:27', '&nbsp;\r\n<h3>Welcome to StageBanter.ca</h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<div style="text-align: center;">\r\n<h4>Discover music venues</h4>\r\n<h4>Find out how to book them</h4>\r\n<h4>Post your opinions about them</h4>\r\n<h4>Connect with other musicians</h4>\r\n<h4>Help each other out!</h4>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\nStart by searching for venues using the form on the left\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>Map of Canadian Venues</strong>\r\n\r\nClicking on the address link takes you to the venue profile page\r\n\r\n[mashup query="post_type=venues" width="100%" height="400px"]\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'Home', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'home', '', '', '2013-06-21 11:55:07', '2013-06-21 15:55:07', '', 0, 'http://stagebanter.ca/?page_id=13', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(376, 1, '2013-04-25 18:59:36', '2013-04-25 22:59:36', '&nbsp;\r\n<h3>\r\nWelcome to StageBanter.ca, start by searching for venues using the form on the left.</p>\r\n</h3><br>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Map of Canadian Venues</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Clicking on the address link takes you to the venue profile page</p> \r\n[mashup query="post_type=venues" width="100%" height="400px"]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '13-revision-28', '', '', '2013-04-25 18:59:36', '2013-04-25 22:59:36', '', 13, 'http://stagebanter.ca/news/13-revision-28/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(14, 1, '2012-11-03 16:46:17', '2012-11-03 20:46:17', '<p>Welcome to StageBanter.ca, start by searching for venues using the form on the left.</p>\n\n<p>If the venue you''re looking for isn''t listed on the site, feel free to add it using the <a href="http://stagebanter.ca/add-a-venue/> add a venue</a> page </p>\n\n<p>Only cities and towns with currently listed venues will come up in the search form.  If the town/city you''re looking for isn''t appearing that means we currently don''t have a venue for that town.  Once a venue is added, that town/city will be listed in the search form</p>\n\n<p>If you wish to leave a review of a venue, just visit that venue''s page, select the number of stars (out of 5) and leave a comment at the bottom</p>\n\n<p>I hope you find StageBanter.ca useful.  I built it to try and make booking a tour just a little less of a pain</p>\n', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '13-revision', '', '', '2012-11-03 16:46:17', '2012-11-03 20:46:17', '', 13, 'http://stagebanter.ca/blog/13-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
