(39, 1, '2012-11-04 00:05:33', '2012-11-04 04:05:33', '<blockquote>Would you like to book (ed. Casa del Popolo)?\r\nAll rooms are usually booked 2 to 3 months in advance.\r\nPlease send any recorded material (cd or cdr) to :\r\n\r\nCasa del Popolo (attn : BOOKING)\r\n4873 boul. St-Laurent,\r\nMontreal, Quebec\r\nH2T 1R6\r\nCanada\r\n\r\nPhone (concerning booking): 514-284-0122 Monday-Friday 10-4pm\r\n\r\nEmail (without attachments): booking[at]casadelpopolo[dot]com\r\nPlease allow 6 to 8 weeks to receive feedback, we receive a lot of mail. We appreciate your patience.\r\n\r\nIf you are booked to play at any of our venues, we can help promote your event:\r\nº Place your flier on our website (the image must conform to approx. 225pixels wide x 300 pixels high)\r\nº Send us a website attachment for the calendar (send us an e-mail that indicates "link for website" with your link and we will place it on the calendar)</blockquote>\r\nsource: <a href="http://www.casadelpopolo.com/contents/casadelpopoloBooking">http://www.casadelpopolo.com/contents/casadelpopoloBooking</a>', 'Casa del Popolo', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'casa-del-popolo', '', '', '2013-04-26 12:38:51', '2013-04-26 16:38:51', '', 0, 'http://stagebanter.ca/?post_type=venues&#038;p=39', 0, 'venues', '', 1),
