(62, 1, '2012-11-15 14:00:57', '2012-11-15 19:00:57', 'Welcome to StageBanter.ca, start by searching for venues using the form on the left.\r\n<br>\r\nIf the venue you''re looking for isn''t listed on the site, feel free to add it using the <a href="&quot;http://stagebanter.ca/add-a-venue/"> add a venue</a> page.\r\n<br>\r\nOnly cities and towns with currently listed venues will come up in the search form. If the town/city you''re looking for isn''t appearing that means we currently don''t have a venue for that town. Once a venue is added, that town/city will be listed in the search form.\r\n<br>\r\nIf you wish to leave a review of a venue, just visit that venue''s page, select the number of stars (out of 5) and leave a comment at the bottom.\r\n<br>\r\nI hope you find StageBanter.ca useful. I built it to try and make booking a tour just a little less of a pain.', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '13-revision-14', '', '', '2012-11-15 14:00:57', '2012-11-15 19:00:57', '', 13, 'http://stagebanter.ca/news/13-revision-14/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
