(71, 1, '2012-11-30 10:32:33', '2012-11-30 15:32:33', 'Jerry Hong / Bookings \r\nQueens Hotel 34 Victoria Crescent Nanaimo\r\nBC, V9R 5B8 \r\njerry@thequeens.ca \r\nTHE BEST WAY TO CONTACT JOEL IS BY EMAIL!!! \r\n\r\nYOU NEED TO SEND US: A copy of your CD / bio\r\n/ references / realistic plan for marketing \r\n\r\nTHE ROOM: 200 seats / full sound system \r\nw/engineer.\r\n3 x 45 min sets \r\nno rooms at venue \r\n\r\n\r\nSource: <a href="http://thequeens.ca/contact.htm">http://thequeens.ca/contact.htm</a>', 'The Queens Hotel', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-queens-hotel', '', '', '2013-04-26 12:37:20', '2013-04-26 16:37:20', '', 0, 'http://stagebanter.ca/?post_type=venues&#038;p=71', 0, 'venues', '', 1),
