(128, 1, '2013-01-05 21:48:59', '2013-01-06 02:48:59', 'Use the form at <a href="http://solsticecafe.ca/contact/performing">http://solsticecafe.ca/contact/performing</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>solstice café</strong> offers a beautiful venue to play your music, speak your poetry, or perform your piece.  if you’re touring in the area and you feel you may have a draw of fans in Victoria, <a href="http://solsticecafe.ca/contact/performers#bookme">please fill in the form</a>, in the meantime, here are some things you should know…\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>we’re not licensed, and all shows are all-ages.</li>\r\n	<li>our seating capacity is up to almost 100 people.</li>\r\n	<li>performers are responsible for promotion of the event, but we will put up show posters that you provide us in the cafe, and add show details to our online accounts (such as Twitter, FaceBook &amp; MySpace).</li>\r\n	<li>performers can sell CDs and other merchandise without a commission charge.</li>\r\n	<li>performers recieve a $10 tab each, up to $50 on any given show night.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\nSource:<a href="http://solsticecafe.ca/contact/performing">http://solsticecafe.ca/contact/performing</a>', 'Solstice Cafe', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'solstice-cafe', '', '', '2013-04-26 12:36:55', '2013-04-26 16:36:55', '', 0, 'http://stagebanter.ca/?post_type=venues&#038;p=128', 0, 'venues', '', 0),
