(132, 1, '2013-01-06 11:44:36', '2013-01-06 16:44:36', '<div id="templatemo_shows_content">\r\n<blockquote>If you are a songwriter and would like to perform at the St. Lawrence Acoustic Stage, send a demo song, CD and/or links to your website, myspace or Youtube performance videos. We consider both touring professional musicians and emerging artists. We present two emerging artist showcases per season (our season runs monthly from September through to May of each year) and between six and seven headliner shows.\r\n\r\nEmerging artists will be considered on the basis of their electronic or other submissions. Please note that we are interested primarily in acoustic performances of original songs. Decisions on emerging artist lineups are usually made one to two months in advance of each show and will involve up to six artists and/or bands.\r\n\r\nHeadliners and openers have almost always been seen in a live performance setting by at least one of our board members before they are booked, we do not make decisions on these shows on the basis of an EPK submission alone. These shows are also usually booked between six months to a full year in advance of scheduled dates. This means, unfortunately, that we are not in a position to offer last minute shows to touring artists coming through our area (no matter how much we love your sound!).\r\n\r\nThanks for your interest in the St. Lawrence Acoustic Stage - we look forward to hearing from you! You will be contacted by a member of our board once the selection process has been completed.\r\n<h5></h5>\r\n<h5>Email EPK, Links or Audio file to:</h5>\r\n<a href="mailto:info@st-lawrencestage.com">info@st-lawrencestage.com</a>\r\n<h5>Mailing address:</h5>\r\nSt. Lawrence Acoustic Stage Performances\r\nBox 3009 Morrisburg ON K0C 1X0</blockquote>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div>Source: <a href="http://www.st-lawrencestage.com/contact.html">http://www.st-lawrencestage.com/contact.html</a></div>', 'St. Lawrence Acoustic Stage', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'st-lawrence-acoustic-stage', '', '', '2013-04-26 12:36:54', '2013-04-26 16:36:54', '', 0, 'http://stagebanter.ca/?post_type=venues&#038;p=132', 0, 'venues', '', 0),
