(134, 1, '2013-01-06 13:44:44', '2013-01-06 18:44:44', '<blockquote>\r\n<div><b>The Bruno Arts Bank</b> venue hosts up to one special event and two original music concerts per month held on either Friday or Saturday nights (twenty seat capacity). For more information please <a href="https://sites.google.com/site/thebrunoartsbank/contact">contact</a> us.  To view our venue photo album please go <a href="http://www.facebook.com/media/set/?set=a.157900817591354.28763.152353278146108&amp;type=3" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">here</a>.  If you are interested in renting the main floor area for a private or public event please contact the Bruno Arts Bank for rates and availability.</div>\r\n<div><b> </b></div>\r\n<div>If you would like to know more about our sound system please go <a href="https://sites.google.com/site/thebrunoartsbank/sound-system">here</a>.</div>\r\n<div></div>\r\n<div>When its warm enough outside, musicians performing at the Arts Bank are invited to stay in our custom built back yard micro A-frame guest house.</div>\r\nThe A-frame can sleep up to four and features an outdoor fire pit, solar convection heater, 120v power and a green roof mini garden viewable from the sleeping loft.  Inside we''ve cozied it up with pillows, quilts afghan blankets, shellac finished pine panelling and reclaimed fir &amp; mahogany boards &amp; cabinetry.</blockquote>\r\n<div></div>\r\n\r\n<div>Source <a href="https://sites.google.com/site/thebrunoartsbank/booking-inquiries">https://sites.google.com/site/thebrunoartsbank/booking-inquiries</a></div>', 'Bruno Arts Bank', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'bruno-arts-bank', '', '', '2013-04-26 12:36:53', '2013-04-26 16:36:53', '', 0, 'http://stagebanter.ca/?post_type=venues&#038;p=134', 0, 'venues', '', 0),
