(192, 1, '2013-01-28 21:10:15', '2013-01-29 02:10:15', '"Like Nothing Else Around !! The Vat Pub! Voted Red Deer''s #1 Place For Live Music for the last 13 Years!!\r\n\r\nNOTICE TO ALL BANDS/ BOOKING AGENTS AND MANAGERS！DO NOT call The Vat Please E-mail VATlive@gmail.com for ALL booking inquiries\r\nDescription\r\nWether you are looking forgreat live music, new friends or, just A pint of our Vat Lager, the Vat Has It All !\r\n\r\nJoin us:\r\nEvery day- Cheap Drinks until 7pm\r\nMondays- All day+night Happy hour Pricing\r\nWednesday- Singer Songwriter night ( your time to shine!)\r\nFriday- LIVE BANDS\r\nSaturday- LIVE BANDS\r\nSunday- JAM NIGHT (sign up jam some tunes!) 9PM start\r\n\r\nCheck back for band listings special events!!\r\n\r\nNOTICE TO ALL BANDS/ BOOKING AGENTS AND MANAGERS！DO NOT call The Vat Please E-mail VATlive@gmail.com for ALL booking inquiries"\r\n\r\nSource: <a href="http://www.facebook.com/pages/The-Vat-Pub/210436822359240?sk=info">http://www.facebook.com/pages/The-Vat-Pub/210436822359240?sk=info</a>', 'The Vat', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-vat', '', '', '2013-04-26 12:35:08', '2013-04-26 16:35:08', '', 0, 'http://stagebanter.ca/?post_type=venues&#038;p=192', 0, 'venues', '', 0),
