(227, 1, '2013-02-04 17:17:00', '2013-02-04 22:17:00', 'StageBanter came about for a number of reasons. It seemed inefficient to us that the best way to find out about venues in an unfamiliar city was to email a band from that city and ask them where to play.  Having hundreds of venues listed in one place speeds up the booking process.  Also, we thought there should be a place where musicians can share their experience at a particular venue, so that someone who''s never been there can know what to expect.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe''re updating the database everyday, so it will continue to grow.  In the meantime, please feel free to <a href="http://stagebanter.ca/add-a-venue/" target="_blank">add any venues</a> you notice are absent from StageBanter.ca.  We will post them as soon as possible.  If you notice any errors, please submit them using the form at the bottom of each venue page.  And if you have something to say about a venue please post it using the comment section at the bottom of each venue page.  Keeping in mind that objective, respectful, and clear comments are the most useful.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nStageBanter is based in Montreal.  If you want to get in touch with us email <a href="mailto:info@stagebanter.ca">info@stagebanter.ca</a>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;', 'About Us', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about-us', '', '', '2013-03-10 15:34:58', '2013-03-10 19:34:58', '', 0, 'http://stagebanter.ca/?page_id=227', 0, 'page', '', 0),
(228, 1, '2013-02-04 17:10:03', '2013-02-04 22:10:03', 'StageBanter came about for a number of reasons. It seemed inefficient to me that the best way to find out about venues in an unfamiliar city was to email a band from that city and ask them.  So  Also, I had some bad experiences at venues and felt there should be a place where I can let other bands know about my experience there.  Obviously the same goes for good experiences, but in this case it was a bad one that inspired the website.\n\n&nbsp;', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '227-revision', '', '', '2013-02-04 17:10:03', '2013-02-04 22:10:03', '', 227, 'http://stagebanter.ca/news/227-revision/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
