(259, 1, '2013-02-16 19:12:16', '2013-02-17 00:12:16', '"The Gateway (or ‘The Gate’, as it is affectionately known) is the on-campus bar at SAIT Polytechnic. Not only is it one of the largest and most successful college bars in Canada, it is also regularly nominated by FFWD Weekly’s ‘Best of Calgary’ in the category of ‘Best Concert Venue, 500+’. The Gate hosts a wide range of events, both large- and small-scale, on a regular basis."\r\n\r\nMarc Thususka, Events & Programming Manager \r\nContact for band bookings and inquiries.\r\n403.210.4378 | marc.thususka@edu.sait.ca\r\n\r\nSource: <a href="http://saitsa.com/eatdrinkshop/thegateway">http://saitsa.com/eatdrinkshop/thegateway</a>', 'The Gateway', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-gateway', '', '', '2013-04-26 12:34:55', '2013-04-26 16:34:55', '', 0, 'http://stagebanter.ca/?post_type=venues&#038;p=259', 0, 'venues', '', 0),
