(338, 1, '2013-04-16 12:37:27', '2013-04-16 16:37:27', '"The Albion Hotel and Wellington Brewery proudly support independent musicians and their efforts to bring their music to the world. The Albion stage features indie acts that range from up and coming talent just starting their musical journey, to signed and recorded artists.\r\nOur Independent Music Series showcases both local and touring bands and artists- If you would like more information on how to inquire about bookings, please contact:info@thealbionhotel.ca"\r\n\r\nSource: <a href="http://www.thealbionhotel.ca/default.asp?id=6&amp;l=1">http://www.thealbionhotel.ca/default.asp?id=6&amp;l=1</a>', 'The Albion Hotel', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-albion-hotel', '', '', '2013-04-26 12:34:25', '2013-04-26 16:34:25', '', 0, 'http://stagebanter.ca/?post_type=venues&#038;p=338', 0, 'venues', '', 0),
