(340, 1, '2013-04-16 11:40:58', '2013-04-16 15:40:58', '"Established 1989, with its name taken from a Clash song, Jimmy Jazz, Guelph, features live entertainment almost every night of the week. Sundays host one of the most popular Open Stage Nights in the city, hosted by local musician Nate Coles. Mondays feature Skydiggers guitarist and Tri-City legend Paul MacLeod. Wellington Breweries, Trailhead Trivia Tuesdays and Name That Tune Wednesdays, are also weekly staples. The rest of the week can be filled by local, Guelph musicians or guests from abroad.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nJimmy Jazz has one of the most diverse musical palettes in Guelph, a patio that’s heated and open year round and a friendly body of regulars that will keep you coming back.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nHours of Operation\r\nOpen 8pm to 2am everyday"\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nSource: <a href="http://www.musiclives.ca/venues/jimmy-jazz/">http://www.musiclives.ca/venues/jimmy-jazz/</a>', 'Jimmy Jazz', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'jimmy-jazz', '', '', '2013-04-26 12:34:25', '2013-04-26 16:34:25', '', 0, 'http://stagebanter.ca/?post_type=venues&#038;p=340', 0, 'venues', '', 0),
(341, 1, '2013-04-16 11:37:20', '2013-04-16 15:37:20', '"Club Vinyl has hosted countless live events. Open primarily weekends, hosting the best in Top 40 DJs, Club Vinyl still opens it’s doors anytime it can to local musicians, or to those passing through town. With the stage at the far end of the building, and intimate capacity, this is the place to see live bands or go dancing."\r\n\r\nSource: <a href="http://www.musiclives.ca/venues/club-vinyl/">http://www.musiclives.ca/venues/club-vinyl/</a>', 'Club Vinyl', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'club-vinyl', '', '', '2013-04-26 12:34:26', '2013-04-26 16:34:26', '', 0, 'http://stagebanter.ca/?post_type=venues&#038;p=341', 0, 'venues', '', 0),
(342, 1, '2013-04-09 12:56:35', '2013-04-09 16:56:35', '<strong>Booking Contact: </strong><a href="mailto:ANAFevents@gmail.com">ANAF Event/Band Booking</a>\r\n\r\n<em id="__mceDel"><strong>Twitter: </strong><a title="Follow the ANAF Guelph on Twitter" href="https://twitter.com/#!/ANAFGuelph" target="_blank">@ANAFGuelph\r\n</a><strong>Facebook: </strong><a title="''Like'' the ANAF Guelph on Facebook" href="http://www.facebook.com/ANAFClub344" target="_blank">ANAF Club 344 Guelph</a></em>\r\n\r\n<strong>Welcome to A.N.A.F. Club 344!</strong>\r\nJoin us for events, parties, dinners, darts and more. Booking your private party or concert has never been easier!\r\n\r\nWe boast a <em>65 inch big screen</em> that can be seen from anywhere in the main room. With speakers throughout and <em>4 professional quality dart boards</em> we’ve got all your sports needs covered! We also have some of the best drink prices in the downtown area! While membership is encouraged, everyone is welcome to come out to have a great time.\r\n\r\nWeekly Events:\r\nMonday: Men’s Darts. 7:30pm.\r\nTuesdays: Women’s Darts. 7pm.\r\nSundays: Youth Darts. 1pm.\r\n\r\n"\r\n\r\nSource: <a href="http://www.musiclives.ca/venues/a-n-a-f-club-344/">http://www.musiclives.ca/venues/a-n-a-f-club-344/</a>', 'ANAF Club 344', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'anaf-club-344', '', '', '2013-04-26 12:34:26', '2013-04-26 16:34:26', '', 0, 'http://stagebanter.ca/?post_type=venues&#038;p=342', 0, 'venues', '', 0),
(343, 1, '2013-03-20 14:19:19', '2013-03-20 18:19:19', '"Established in 1994, with a great location and casual vibe, Van Gogh’s Ear remains in the hub of downtown Guelph’s entertainment district. With a concentration on local music, and the addition of The Loft on third floor, the building resonates with a unique musical history. Chances are that your favourite live entertainment, whether it be a solo artist, band or DJ, has appeared at Van Gogh’s Ear at some point.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nRecently VGE’s, as it is also known, added full restaurant service, catered by Salsateria, to it’s main floor. Featuring a Latin spin on pizza, and homemade salsas and wraps, the addition brought with it a flavour that cannot be mistaken. With weekend breakfasts starting at 9am and a new main floor patio, Van Gogh’s Ear has a lot more to offer than just a great place to see live music.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nHours of Operation\r\nMonday to Friday 11am to 2am\r\nSaturday 9am to 2am\r\nSunday 9am to 10pm"\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nSource: <a href="http://www.musiclives.ca/venues/vangoghsear/">http://www.musiclives.ca/venues/vangoghsear/</a>', 'Van Gogh''s Ear', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'van-goghs-ear', '', '', '2013-04-26 12:34:27', '2013-04-26 16:34:27', '', 0, 'http://stagebanter.ca/?post_type=venues&#038;p=343', 0, 'venues', '', 0),
