(414, 1, '2013-06-06 14:41:12', '2013-06-06 18:41:12', '<h1>LIVE MUSIC &amp; EVENTS</h1>\r\nCome join us and enjoy the work of talented local and traveling musicians. We''ll surprise you with a great variety of musical styles, including rock, blues, pop and jazz.\r\n<h2>GRANVILLE STREET</h2>\r\n<b>Every Thursday night: Open mic night 8:00pm-10:00pm</b>\r\n\r\nThursday night is open mic night, hosted by <a href="http://www.evmusik.com/" target="_blank">Ev</a>. You''ll never know what you''ll get, as a variety of performers drop in for a set. Everything from music to spoken word, and even stand-up comedy acts could be on stage.\r\n\r\nCheck out the <a href="http://facebook.com/TreesOpenMicShowcase" target="_blank">Open Mic Facebook page</a> for more details or enquiries.\r\n\r\n<b>Every Friday night: Live music 8:00pm-10:00pm</b>\r\n\r\nOur longtime host and local music legend <a href="http://johnpippus.com/" target="_blank">John Pippus</a> continues to showcase local talent every Friday night. Scroll down for a list of upcoming acts.\r\n\r\nContact <a href="mailto:jpippus@gmail.com">John Pippus</a> for booking enquiries.\r\n<h2>GASTOWN</h2>\r\nEvery Saturday night during the summer (June 1st – September 28th) from 7:00-9:00 pm at our<a title="Locations" href="http://www.treescoffee.com/about-us/locations/">Gastown café on Water Street</a> in downtown Vancouver.\r\n\r\nContact <a href="mailto:treesmusicgastown@gmail.com">Marq DeSouza</a> for booking enquiries.\r\n\r\nScroll down for a list of upcoming music nights and performers.\r\n\r\n<article>\r\n<h2><a title="Open Mic Night" href="http://www.treescoffee.com/events/open-mic-night-18/">THU JUN 6 FROM 8:00PM TO 10:00PM</a></h2>\r\n<h3>granville</h3>\r\n<b>Every Thursday night: Open mic night 8:00pm-10:00pm</b>\r\n\r\nThursday night is open mic night, hosted by <a href="http://www.evmusik.com/" target="_blank">Ev</a>. You’ll never know what you’ll get, as a variety of performers drop in for a set. Everything from music to spoken word, and even stand-up comedy acts could be on stage.\r\n\r\n<a href="http://www.treescoffee.com/blog/2013/01/open-mic-night-at-trees-organic/">Click here for more details</a>\r\n\r\nSign up starts at 7:30pm.\r\n\r\n</article>\r\n\r\nSource<a href="http://www.treescoffee.com/events/">http://www.treescoffee.com/events/</a>', 'Trees Organic Coffee and Roasting House', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'trees-organic-coffee-and-roasting-house', '', '', '2013-06-06 14:41:12', '2013-06-06 18:41:12', '', 0, 'http://stagebanter.ca/?post_type=venues&#038;p=414', 0, 'venues', '', 0),
(415, 1, '2013-06-10 11:05:15', '2013-06-10 15:05:15', '<blockquote>To open for our house bands or play\r\nour Canadian content night email\r\nyour epk to:\r\n<a href="mailto:music@roxyvan.com">music@roxyvan.com</a>\r\n(604) 331-7999</blockquote>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nSource: <a href="http://www.roxyvan.com/home.php">http://www.roxyvan.com/home.php</a>', 'The Roxy Cabaret', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-roxy-cabaret', '', '', '2013-06-10 11:05:15', '2013-06-10 15:05:15', '', 0, 'http://stagebanter.ca/?post_type=venues&#038;p=415', 0, 'venues', '', 2),
(416, 1, '2013-06-10 13:04:08', '2013-06-10 17:04:08', '<blockquote>For National, Local &amp; Regional Booking inquiries as-well as press inquiries please contact<a href="mailto:blake.mcritchie@gmail.com" target="_blank">blake.mcritchie@gmail.com</a>\r\n\r\nLOCAL BOOKING INQUIRIES\r\nPlease submit an Electronic Press Kit (EPK) with audio samples that best represent your music. In the email please include the following info:\r\n\r\n- Describe your music (genre, influences, etc)\r\n- References are important. Please give a detailed history of your previous performance history in the Vancouver/ Canadian market along with any relevant references from venues, promoters, etc.\r\n- Your average draw on a weekday\r\n- Other bands you go well with locally\r\n\r\nNote : * this venue is designed to handle both Live music and DJ based shows*</blockquote>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nSource: <a href="http://redroomonrichards.com/contact?&PHPSESSID=4e85f11256723ba7956404c3b8abd54c">http://redroomonrichards.com/contact</a>', 'Red Room Ultrabar', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'red-room-ultrabar', '', '', '2013-06-10 13:04:08', '2013-06-10 17:04:08', '', 0, 'http://stagebanter.ca/?post_type=venues&#038;p=416', 0, 'venues', '', 0),
