(424, 1, '2013-06-16 22:13:18', '2013-06-17 02:13:18', '<blockquote>"As I''m sure you can appreciate, The Cellar Restaurant / Jazz Club receives numerous solicitations for gigs. I appreciate the interest in playing our establishment. Please feel free to drop off or mail your package here and address it to Cory Weeds. If you wish you may include a self addressed stamped envelope and I would gladly mail the package back to you as I understand the costs of these packages. I will get around to listening to your CDs but be forewarned that I have a stack of about 30 at time and can only listen to so many at a time. We are also usually booked three months in advance.\r\n\r\nUpon listening if there is something that is of interest I will gladly call or email you. Please do not leave messages on The Cellar''s machine asking if I have received the package or if I have listened to it. Please do not ask for me personally when you drop your package off. You can leave it with a staff member and I can assure you I will get it.\r\n\r\nThanks for your understanding,\r\nCory\r\n\r\nSource: <a href="http://www.cellarjazz.com/index.cfm?go=site.info">http://www.cellarjazz.com/index.cfm?go=site.info</a></blockquote>', 'The Cellar', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'the-cellar', '', '', '2013-06-16 22:13:18', '2013-06-17 02:13:18', '', 0, 'http://stagebanter.ca/?post_type=venues&#038;p=424', 0, 'venues', '', 0),
