(464, 1, '2013-07-26 19:40:12', '2013-07-26 23:40:12', 'Hey Erick,\n\nSorry for my slow reply.  Somehow, I wasn''t or missed the notification that you had posted.  Most smaller bands in canada just do their own booking.  They just call and email venues and try and get booked.  It''s a good idea to be contacting venues at least 3 months in advance of the date. \n\nBooking venues isn''t fun, a lot of places won''t respond.  But you can be reasonably persistent.  Follow the directions that are listed on their site or on here if they''re available. \n\nPlaces will encourage you to link up with local bands for shows. They want to make sure there will be a reasonable crowd. It''s a good idea anyway. \n\nSo that''s it, yes you can book your own venues. Be careful of places that seem to have complicated deals. It should be fairly simple like a percentage of the door or a flat rate to play or free to play.\n\nAll the best!', 'Reply To: Montreal', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'reply-to-montreal-2', '', '', '2013-07-26 19:40:12', '2013-07-26 23:40:12', '', 456, 'http://stagebanter.ca/forums/reply/reply-to-montreal-2/', 2, 'reply', '', 0),
(465, 26, '2013-07-26 23:19:11', '2013-07-27 03:19:11', 'Design A Smarter Website Using These Handy Tips 4079\n\n<a href="http://eon.businesswire.com/news/eon/20130411005444/en/mypcbackup/mypcbackup-review"><img alt="online backup reviews" src="http://researched-reviews.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/04/mypcbackup1.png" width="364" height="210" /></a>\n\n<strong><a href="http://eon.businesswire.com/news/eon/20130411005444/en/mypcbackup/mypcbackup-review">online backup reviews</a></strong>&lt;/p&gt;\n\nIf you want a website to achieve success, it all boils down to design. However, as there is so much information on the market about website design, and since that information is constantly evolving, it may be hard to find out the easiest way to create good websites. This is a a valuable thing that you have come across this article. This information has the latest, effective tips you can get on website design.\n\nIt is very important test the web pages inside your website to be sure they search as they should on every different browser a prosperous site needs to display correctly in all browsers. An internet site that works on Internet Explorer might not display directly in Firefox, Google Chrome, or Safari. Prior to deciding to website is launched, test the display of each page in every major browsers.\n\nAllow users to cancel action if they wish to do it. Actions include registering for almost any e-mail notifications, browsing the web page, or submitting forms. You can deter people from returning to your blog if you don''t allow them the choice of cancelling things these are in the middle of completing.\n\nNever use pop-ups. Viewers hate pop-ups they may be annoying and unprofessional. Many people will leave a site containing pop-ups, even the big sites. Ensure your clients are pleased by eliminating these pesky ads from your site. When you are needed by your hosting company to have pop-up ads, you might want to consider obtaining a new web host.\n\nPrevent utilizing pop-ups on your site. Everyone hates getting pop-up after pop-up online. Most people will leave an internet site when it contains pop-ups, even though these internet websites are extremely large ones. Avoid annoying ads to make certain your potential customers revisit again. In case your host will give you no choice about using pop-ups, you almost certainly must choose a completely new one.\n\nWhen choosing what background color to use for your blog, white is a superb and effective choice. White backgrounds make copy far more easily readable and offer your web site an even more mature look. Should there be a much more complicated design from the background, it could be very distracting, and make your internet site look less professional. It is usually preferable to experience a simple background.\n\nDo not have pop-up windows on the site. While popup adverts can assist you to generate some income from your website, also, they are very likely to frustrate your online visitors. Actually, you could possibly drive those to leave your site out of irritation and frustration with the pop-ups. You could potentially lose visitors for a lifetime.\n\nWhite is a great selection for a background color. It''s simplistic, yet provides extensive potential at adding flare and color elsewhere. A bright, white background makes it easier to read through text in addition, it appears more professional. Conversely, complex backgrounds distract out of your content to make your website seem a lot less professional. It is best to keep with an easy background while you are designing your site.\n\nYou might have heard about software like Photoshop and how you can create amazing designs together. However, Dreamweaver is less popular, and so many people are unaware of the advantages it has for web site designers. It''s important to reach know this application and discover how it could aid your design.\n\nMake certain your entire domains, including sub-domains, include visible taglines. They must be bold and large so the viewer can see them. It requires to explain exactly what the page is around so your visitor can easily plan to stick around or otherwise not.\n\nBegin small once you begin off building your websites. This method for you to ascertain the things that work well and exactly what does not, and it will be easy to enhance your skills based on that. Learn from your successes and your mistakes as you may expand your blog.\n\nFileZilla is a wonderful file server, and yes it gives you the opportunity program your domain, username, and port settings directly into its quick menu. By doing this, when you log back on the server, all that you should do is select your personalized settings through the menu. This should help you save your time.\n\nUse a basic layout that will help you develop a website design foundation where to construct. This basic design will allow you to grasp the straightforward stuff, which can prepare you to tackle sophisticated website design principles with time.\n\nYou are going to design a better site if you keep learning all the way. While you are confident in your abilities to utilize one technique, you should then move on to mastering the following skill. This can lengthen enough time it requires to develop your initial site, but you''ll learn to expertly crank them out as soon as you''re done.\n\nAgain, you have to start your web design study by learning the essentials of proper web page design. You would like your websites to both work correctly and look nice. You can find a great deal of available resources, making it difficult to find a proper place to start. You can aquire a jump start by utilizing the insights given here.', 'Discover How To Design Websites Similar To A Pro 5544', '', 'spam', 'closed', 'open', '', 'discover-how-to-design-websites-similar-to-a-pro-5544', '', '', '2013-07-26 23:19:11', '2013-07-27 03:19:11', '', 452, 'http://stagebanter.ca/forums/topic/discover-how-to-design-websites-similar-to-a-pro-5544/', 0